node.text:
Day 30 of Circuit Breaker. ⁣
⁣
Couldn’t get a cake for Mother Day’s celebration? No worries! You can still show your love by sending some Bento sets from @Wangthaikitchen to her. ⁣
⁣
Mother’s Day Special sets range from $16 to $18.80 comes with a choice of Thai Iced Milk Tea or Lime Juice.⁣ (Swipe to see) Add on $28 for a bouquet of dried flowers to surprise her! 💐⁣
⁣⁣
Islandwide available now! Swipe to see how to order. Or call 63582938/93847588 for more information! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Thank you Nelly @PopstarMedia for delivering the bouquet and yummy bentos and Chef Ivan @WangThaiKitchen for the delicious meal. ⁣
⁣⁣
📍 𝕎𝕒𝕟𝕘 𝕋𝕙𝕒𝕚 𝕂𝕚𝕥𝕔𝕙𝕖𝕟 旺泰小厨⁣⁣⁣
Blk 92 Toa Payoh Lorong 4⁣⁣⁣
Unit No.: 01-274⁣⁣⁣
Singapore 310092⁣⁣⁣
Tel No.: 6358 2938⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
